              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-summaries-margin"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <br>
    <br>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="container">
  <center>
    <p>

    <h3>A platform that opens doors to your Freshman year.</h3>
    </p>
    <p>

    <h3>Get the <span class="knock-text-color"> application essays</span>, <span class="knock-text-color">resumes</span>, and <span class="knock-text-color">everything you need to know</span> from the students themselves.</h3>
    </p>
  </center>

  <br/>

  <p>How it works:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      High School Seniors:
      <ul>
        <li>
          <%=link_to "View current students and schedule a call", view_application_essays_index_path%>
        </li>
        <li>Enjoy getting an inside look at the college application process like never before</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <br/>
    <li>
      Georgetown Students:
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="/">Upload your credentials</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          Specify whether you'd additionally like to monetize your time through in-person, video, or phone meetings
        </li>
        <li>Enjoy a passive source of income&nbsp;</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <br/><br/>

  <% @essays.each_slice(2) do |group| %>
      <div class="summary-thumbnail img-wrapper home-essay-list-item" style="overflow: hidden;">
        <div class="row">
          <% group.each do |e| %>
              <div class="col-md-2 home-image-padding">
                <img class="img-thumbnail home-image-list-image" src="<%=real_img_or_gu_logo e.your_pic_path.url  %>" style="margin-top: 30px;">
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <article>
                  <header>
                    <h5><%= link_to "#{e.author.upcase}", view_application_essays_show_essay_path(essay_id: e.id) %></h5>
                    <p class="knock-text-color">$5.00</p>
                  </header>
                  <p><span class="knock-text-color">Philanthrophic Option:</span> A portion of this student's earnings go to the Georgetown Scholarship Fund</p>
                  <p><span class="knock-text-color">High School Tags:</span>Student Government President,
                  Varsity Tennis,
                  Theater</p>
                </article>
              </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br/>
  <% end %>
  <%= paginate @essays %>
  <br/><br/>

  <p class="global-disclaimer">Disclaimer: Georgetown has plagiarism checks for every application submitted. Highschoolers are made well aware that any copying will be easily detected and they alone are responsible resulting in a rejected application. Your essay is merely a storytelling template.</p>
</div>